Sentencas: A new type of oxygen ion conductor Gd0.1Ce0.9O1.95 (GDC) modified La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-delta (LSCF) electrode is developed for proton conducting solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs).
Titulo: New insight into highly active cathode of proton conducting solid oxide fuel cells by oxygen ionic conductor modification

Sentencas: The modified LSCF electrode by nano GDC particles on BZCY electrolytes shows high performance.
Titulo: New insight into highly active cathode of proton conducting solid oxide fuel cells by oxygen ionic conductor modification

Sentencas: The power density of the single cell using GDC modified LSCF electrode at 700 degrees C is 782 mW cm(-2), which is higher than those of other electrodes.
Titulo: New insight into highly active cathode of proton conducting solid oxide fuel cells by oxygen ionic conductor modification

Sentencas: The encouraging results open a potential way to develop cathode materials for proton conducting SOFCs.
Titulo: New insight into highly active cathode of proton conducting solid oxide fuel cells by oxygen ionic conductor modification
